## 3. Typography

**Pairing:** [Display family] / [Body family]
**Source:** Self-hosted woff2 in `/fonts/`. **Never** load from `fonts.googleapis.com`.

| Style | Family | Size | Weight | Tracking | Line-height |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Display (h1) | [Instrument Serif] | clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem) | 400 | -0.03em | 1.0 |
| Heading (h2) | [Instrument Serif] | clamp(1.875rem, 3.5vw, 3rem) | 400 | -0.025em | 1.05 |
| Subheading (h3) | [Geist] | 1.25rem | 600 | -0.015em | 1.2 |
| Body | [Geist] | 1rem | 400 | 0 | 1.65 |
| Small / Meta | [Geist] | 0.875rem | 400 | 0.01em | 1.5 |
| Caption | [Geist] | 0.75rem | 500 | 0.04em (uppercase) | 1.4 |

**Rules:**
- 2 families maximum.
- 2–4 weights total across both families.
- Body measure: 60–75ch.

