## 4. Component Stylings

### Buttons

| Variant | Background | Text | Border | Hover | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Primary | `--color-accent` | `--color-bg` | none | `--color-accent-hover` + `translateY(-1px)` | CTA only, max 1 per viewport |
| Secondary | transparent | `--color-text` | 1px `--color-border` | `--color-surface-2` background | Supporting actions |
| Ghost | transparent | `--color-text-muted` | none | `--color-text` color | Tertiary, in-flow links |

All buttons:
- Padding: `0.875rem 1.5rem`
- Border-radius: `[2px / 4px / 999px depending on direction]`
- Font: body family, 500 weight, 0.9375rem
- Transition: `transform 150ms ease-out, background-color 200ms ease-out`
- `:focus-visible` → 2px outline in `--color-focus-ring`, 2px offset

### Cards

- Background: `--color-surface`
- Border: 1px `--color-border` OR shadow (pick one, never both)
- Padding: `1.5rem` mobile, `2rem` desktop
- Border-radius: `[match button radius scale]`

### Inputs

- Background: `--color-bg`
- Border: 1px `--color-border`, focus → 1px `--color-accent`
- Padding: `0.75rem 1rem`
- Label: always present and associated, never placeholder-as-label

### Navigation

- Height: 64px desktop, 56px mobile
- Background: `--color-bg` with optional `backdrop-filter: blur(12px)` on scroll
- Border-bottom: appears on scroll only, 1px `--color-border`

