## 6. Depth & Elevation

Three explicit layers. No flat-everything, no shadow-everything.

| Layer | Surface | Shadow | Use |
|---|---|---|---|
| Base | `--color-bg` | none | Page background |
| Elevated | `--color-surface` | `0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)` | Cards, inline panels |
| Floating | `--color-surface` | `0 12px 32px -8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)` | Modals, dropdowns, sticky nav on scroll |

**Texture (optional):** [grain overlay at 3% opacity / noise SVG / none]

